<div id="pf65f2" class="pf w64 h340" data-page-no="65f2"><div class="pc pc65f2 w64 h340"><div class="t m1f8 x25 h8c y18e5 ff4 fs31 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">LIGHT </div><div class="t m18fb x25 h8c y1119 ff4 fs31 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">FOR A </div><div class="t m86c x25 h8c y12af ff4 fs31 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">DARK </div><div class="t m410 xc2 h8c y1cdd ff4 fs31 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">WORLD </div><div class="t m1737 x63 h25e y2cdb ff1 fs73 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">A </div><div class="t m1311 xb h16b y2c1d ff1 fs3d fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">book about the </div><div class="t m1490 x3 h16b y2b1c ff1 fs3d fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">Sabbath that will radically </div><div class="t m2f85 x4a h16b y2285 ff1 fs3d fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">revolutionize your life! </div><div class="t m349 x7d h4c y1e56 ff4 fs19 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">For many Christians, the Sabbath </div><div class="t mcfd x80 h4c y13e1 ff4 fs19 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">doctrine has been taught and practiced </div><div class="t m49 x98 h4c ybcb ff4 fs19 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">only in the context of which day is the </div><div class="t m1e5 x98 h4c y1046 ff4 fs19 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">right day to worship on. But does the </div><div class="t mf34 x97 h4c y10b6 ff4 fs19 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">Sabbath have any relevance to contem-</div><div class="t m802 x97 h4c ybcd ff4 fs19 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">porary life? </div><div class="t m766 x79 h4c y1c9b ff4 fs19 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">Greg Nelson believes the Sabbath is </div><div class="t m19ee x43 h4c y1c29 ff4 fs19 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">not only relevant but revolutionary. With </div><div class="t m311 x2 h4c y14d5 ff4 fs19 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">a passion for turning biblical truths </div><div class="t m64b x9e h4c y1563 ff4 fs19 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">inside out and revealing the impact those </div><div class="t m632 x68 h4c y14d6 ff4 fs19 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">truths can make on our lives, Nelson tack-</div><div class="t m192c x68 h4c y1488 ff4 fs19 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">les questions like: </div><div class="t m10d8 x68 h4c y1e08 ff4 fs19 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">• </div><div class="t m639 x3a h4c y1e08 ff4 fs19 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">How does our Sabbath keeping impact </div><div class="t m11d x1d h4c y15d0 ff4 fs19 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">our family relationships, hurting people, </div><div class="t m9c2 x47 h4c y1566 ff4 fs19 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">and the environment? </div><div class="t m10d8 xbd h4c y418 ff4 fs19 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">• </div><div class="t m1147 x27 h4c y418 ff4 fs19 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">What does the Sabbath say about our responsibility to God&apos;s cre-</div><div class="t m873 xbd h4c y1b31 ff4 fs19 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">ation? </div><div class="t m10d8 x4 h4c y1657 ff4 fs19 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">• </div><div class="t m14b0 x11 h4c y748 ff4 fs19 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">How does a true understanding of God&apos;s Sabbath impact our </div><div class="t mea3 xbd h4c y986 ff4 fs19 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">experience of the Sabbath and how we use it to experience God </div><div class="t m683 xbd h4c y987 ff4 fs19 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">more completely? </div><div class="t m135 x26 h4c y1c6b ff4 fs19 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">Through dynamic illustrations and the input from a wide variety </div><div class="t mf45 xbd h4c y1ce5 ff4 fs19 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">of contemporary authors, A </div><div class="t m146 x2e h16 y1ec1 ff6 fs7 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">Touch of Heaven </div><div class="t m12e x57 h4c y1ec1 ff4 fs19 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">puts forth fresh para-</div><div class="t m466 x4 h4c yeac ff4 fs19 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">digms for the day of rest that transform it into a powerful tool for </div><div class="t m44a xbd h4c y19d7 ff4 fs19 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">Church and personal renewal. </div><div class="t m1cf6 x4 h4c y14dc ff4 fs19 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">Paperback. 0-8163-1721-6 </div><div class="t m1533 x4 h4c y1ce8 ff4 fs19 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">US$12.99, Cdn$19.49 </div><div class="t m229b x4 h38 y1121 ff1 fs18 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">From Pacific Press®. </div><div class="t m547 x4 h38 yeb4 ff1 fs18 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">We have what you want. </div><div class="t mbd0 x4 h4c y1c72 ff4 fs19 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">Available at your local Adventist Boo